    <briefdescription>
<para>this object stores a difference between two meshes: both in coordinates and in topology </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>if the meshes are similar then this object is small, if the meshes are very distinct then this object will be even larger than one mesh itself Generated from class <computeroutput><ref refid="classMR_1_1MeshDiff" kindref="compound">MR.MeshDiff</ref></computeroutput>. This is the non-const half of the class. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
